# Production Hardening — Walkthrough (FINAL 10/10)

All 10 critical structural improvements from the `SYSTEM_AUDIT_LOG` have been successfully implemented, bringing the application up to true production grade.

## Changes Made

### Phase 1: Security & Database Foundational Hardening
| ID | Severity | File | Fix |
|---|---|---|---|
| SEC-01 | **Critical** | [route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/students/route.ts) | Restored admin auth check (`if (false)` → proper role gate) |
| DB-01 | High | [User.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/User.ts) | Added `{ batch, rollNumber }` unique sparse index |
| DB-02 | Medium | [Attendance.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Attendance.ts) | Added `records.student` index for fast dashboard queries |
| LOG-01 | High | [tests/[id]/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/tests/%5Bid%5D/route.ts) | Eliminated TOCTOU race — atomic [create](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/actions/academic.ts#121-131) with E11000 catch |
| LOG-02 | Medium | Same file | Shuffled options now re-labeled A→D sequentially |
| UI-01 | Medium | [tests/[id]/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28student%29/student/tests/%5Bid%5D/page.tsx) | Timer uses absolute `endTime` — immune to tab throttling |
| API-01 | Medium | [payments/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/finance/payments/route.ts) | Added [page](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/gtag.ts#13-22)/`limit` pagination |
| API-02 | Medium | [admin/tests/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/tests/route.ts) | Added [page](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/gtag.ts#13-22)/`limit` pagination |

### Phase 2: Memory Safeties & Database Atomicity
| ID | Severity | File | Fix |
|---|---|---|---|
| API-03 | High | [tests/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/tests/route.ts) | Added a hard 2MB limit on `questionsFile` and `answersFile` JSON uploads. Prevents 1GB file malicious attacks from exhausting and crashing Node.js V8 RAM limits entirely. |
| TXN-01 | High | [payments/[studentId]/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/finance/payments/%5BstudentId%5D/route.ts) | Refactored fee payment deletions to use purely atomic MongoDB ops (`$pull` and `$inc`). Eliminates potential race condition corruption from concurrent manual array splicing, securing exact decimal balance integrity. |

