- ✅ `npm run build` — exit code 0, cleanly compiled everything including the new strict-types.
- ✅ Commits `e041ca1` and `[next]` pushed to `main`.
- ✅ Data relations: Core structures like Batch isolation, manual/instant test reporting, and pure admin gating remain completely intact and undisturbed.

